    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice</strong>, a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and 225ml [300ml] <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
