            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mince has browned, add your<strong> cornflour</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> ginger paste</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>agave</strong>, then return the <strong>softened peppers</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until sticky and the meat-free mince is cooked through</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
