        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince is sticky, remove the pan from the heat, sprinkle over the <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>sticky sesame meat-free stir-fry</strong></p>",
